==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: overlearn
<hw>o`ver*learn"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To learn (a
fact or skill) repetitively, beyond the point where it can be
immediately recalled; in experimental psychology, to continue to learn
beyond the point where the criterion of adequate learning has been
reached.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>overlearned</ent>⟦br⟧
